text: pitisara arabivarungen samaharak (yuddhayata nogos sitimata) taman venuven anumætiya illannaha. ehet allahvada, ohuge dutayavada boru kala aya nam, (anumætiya noillama nivasehi) vadi gatha. ebævin movungen vu (mema) pratiksepa karannanva itamat ikmanin itamat vedana gena dena danduvama vit sendu vanu æta
